# Rindle: `rindle render`/`up`/`deploy` regenerate these from rindle.ncl. Ignore the renders, but
# COMMIT the cloud binding (.rindle/cloud.json) — it's what re-attaches deploys to our headwaters
# app instead of provisioning a duplicate (deploy.rs: `POST /api/apps` is not idempotent).
/rindle.json
/.rindle/*
!/.rindle/cloud.json

# Private commercial overlay (marketing site + Stripe billing). Kept OUT of the open-source tree; it's
# its own private repo cloned/symlinked in here, merged into the build via the #commercial seam.
# See docs/COMMERCIAL_OVERLAY.md.
commercial/
!src/commercial/
!src/commercial/stub.ts
